settings.introduction: Everybody wants the best for their pets. Their health and happiness is of critical importance to us but with so much information available it can be difficult to know where to turn. That's why we've created Ask The Expert, where we aim to answer your questions. Simply email hello@getsetpet.com with any questions you have!

settings.image_text_under_richtext:
Hi there!

We’re Martin and Jason, the founders of Get Set Pet, and we’re on a journey to change the way you buy pet supplies.

Although one of us is a dedicated dog lover and the other is still searching for the cat of his dreams, we discovered we had similar concerns when it came to finding reliable information about pet care – especially in relation to food. Do big-name brands contain all the nutrients Max the dog needs? Is raw food suitable for a house cat? Where can I go to get honest advice?

settings.image_text_block_richtext:
With no unbiased answers immediately at our fingertips, our pet project (so to speak) was born. 

We’re focused on creating a world where pet health and happiness comes first. Our vision is for Get Set Pet to be more than just a pet shop. We believe it should be simple to get everything your pet needs in one place – so you spend more time enjoying their company and less time worrying about their wellbeing.

As an independent company, we source the highest-quality products available, while providing the essential details you need to make informed decisions, whether you have a cat, dog, small mammal, bird or reptile. 

Working with a panel of experts in a range of fields, we aim to make your life easier. From nutritional values to pricing, we provide the most relevant product details in a clear, easy-to-digest format, so you don’t have to hunt for answers online. Plus, our blog is filled with additional advice and tips, so you can help your pet live its best life.

Of course, we know there will be times when you’re unsure what to do; whether you’ve just got your first pet or you’re an old hand, you might need a little reassurance. That’s why we’ve set up live chat, so you can ask our team questions, just like you would at your local store.

Come to think of it, exceptional customer service comes as standard at Get Set Pet. As a pair of technology lovers, we use the latest digital tools to create a first-class shopping experience. From providing expert information, to delivering the top-notch products and keeping you in the loop with the latest in pet care, your best friend is at the heart of everything we do.

And for those pets yet to find their forever home, we’re giving back. We’re supporting sanctuaries up and down the UK, helping them care for animals in need. These small charities do sterling work, so it’s the least we can do. 

Join us on our journey to a world of pet wellbeing.

settings.title: The Pet Food Pioneers
settings.text: A pioneering pet food brand, we've been at the forefront of the healthy pet food market since the company was founded by veterinary surgeon John Burns in 1993. We specialise in using simple, healthy and wholesome ingredients to create award-winning recipes almost 30 years ago, we've released a variety of healthy and hypoallergenic pet food ranges, all using a single protein source and ingredients that are as healthy, wholesome and sustainable as possible

settings.title: Britain's Favourite Dog Food AGAIN!
settings.text: Which? surveyed 3,122 of their members to discover the most delicious dog foods you can buy in 2022. "Burns was the most-loved brand for the second year in a row, and is also a good-value option!" You could potentially save around £80 a year if you switched to Burns.

settings.title: Benefits
settings.text: Burns will never compromise on our belief that high-quality ingredients and good nutrition can really make a difference to the overall happiness and wellbeing of each pet. That's why we continue to make the same nutritious recipes that pets love, using simple, wholesome and healthy ingredients

settings.title: Welcome Big Dog World Customers
settings.text: We are very excited to welcome all Big Dog World customers to the Get Set Pet family.  We promise to deliver you the same great range of products and brilliant customer service you deserve. As a welcome offer, we would like to provide you with 10% off your first order with discount code BDW10.

settings.title: Passing The Big Dog Baton
settings.text: "After 12 years of running Big Dog World, I felt it was time for a change. Having taken the decision to move on to a new project, I knew I wouldn’t sell the company to just anyone. I wanted to ensure our loyal and valued customers would be well looked after and Get Set Pet fit the bill. I feel completely confident that Martin, Jason and their team will offer you the same level of exceptional service that I have strived to provide for the last 12 years." - Neil Stanton, Founder of Big Dog World

settings.title: A Warm Welcome from Jason and Martin (Founders of Get Set Pet)
settings.text: On behalf of the entire team, we are thrilled to welcome you to Get Set Pet and look forward to providing you with a great customer experience and a smooth transition from Big Dog World. We're eager to hear from you all as we commence this exciting journey together. As a welcome offer, we would like to provide you with 10% off your first order with discount code BDW10. Thank you in advance for your ongoing support and custom. - Jason Phillips (pictured left), and Martin Ruddy (pictured right)

settings.title: Joining the Get Set Pet Family
settings.text: The only UK specialist for everything large and giant breed dogs has joined Get Set Pet! We’ll be continuing to provide you with your favourite premium large breed dog foods including: Royal Canin, James Wellbeloved, Arden Grange, Orijen, Acana, Barking Heads, Dog's Dinner, Burns, and Taste of the Wild. You can now also get all of these on a regular basis, using our Get Set Save subscription service. Plus, you can still get super tough dog toys and chews, large dog beds, bigger dog coats, health products, and grooming supplies – now with Get Set Pet’s top-rated customer experience! Please don't hesitate to get in touch if you have any questions. You can chat to us via the chat function on our website or email us at hello@getsetpet.com.

settings.title: Why invest in us?
settings.text: Since our last Seedrs raise in early 2021, our business has grown rapidly. We now have over 1,200 subscription customers, our annual turnover has more than doubled and we have seen an increase in subscription revenue of 173% YOY. Our goal is to accelerate our strong growth whilst raising the customer experience bar even further.

settings.text: At Get Set Pet we’re on a mission to help your pets live their best lives. We bring together expert knowledge, nutritious food and high-quality products and combine it with an exceptional customer experience. Whilst others talk about it, we deliver and our results speak for themselves.  Get Set Pet is the UK’s #1 rated pet supplies business on Reviews.io, where we have received over 2,200 5-star customer reviews with an overall rating of 5/5.

settings.text: We’re really excited about what the future holds for Get Set Pet and we hope that you might consider joining us on our journey. You can invest as little as £50.74. All you need to do is login/create an account on Seedrs and follow the steps to make your investment. We’d love to have you onboard!
